TY  - JOUR
TI  - Equilibrium in a Finite Sequence of Markets with Transaction Cost
AU  - Kurz, Mordecai
AB  - [The work extends the results of an earlier paper by Hahn; it presents a model of a barter economy with a sequence of markets in which each trader operates with his own transaction technology. An equilibrium is proved to exist and the efficiency of equilibrium is discussed.]
