TY  - JOUR
TI  - Recontracting Stability
AU  - Feldman, Allan M.
AB  - [This paper contains a relatively simple proof for the stability of Edgeworthian recontracting. It also applies that proof to a random recontracting process in an economy with a finite number of utility vectors, in which the recontracting process is a Markov chain and all non-core utility vectors correspond to transient states.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1974
